text: Blabicentrus martinsi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Dalens, Touroult and Tavakilian in 2009.BioLib.cz - Blabicentrus martinsi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphorini Category:Beetles described in 2009
